      "content": "it just feels like i'm waiting for something that's never coming back. i look at the empty side of the bed and it's so obvious that the world moved on but i'm just stuck in this version of reality that makes no sense. i don't even see the point in trying to \"fix\" it or find \"support\" when the only person who made life worth living is gone. it feels like i'm just punishing myself by staying here.",
